ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: How does the toilet paper trading app work?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our app connects toilet paper buyers and sellers in a user-friendly marketplace. You can list your excess rolls, browse available stock, and make trades with other users in your area.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: Is it safe to trade toilet paper through the app?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Yes, we prioritize user safety. All transactions are contactless, and we provide guidelines for hygienic exchanges. Users are also rated based on their trading history.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: What types of toilet paper can I trade on the app?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Our app supports trading of all types of toilet paper, from standard rolls to luxury quilted options. You can specify brand, ply count, and other details when listing or searching for products.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: How do I get started with toilet paper trading?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Simply download our app, create an account, and start browsing or listing toilet paper. You can set your preferred trading radius and receive notifications when matches are available in your area.

FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: Is it safe to trade toilet paper through the app?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Absolutely! We prioritize user safety with secure in-app messaging, verified user profiles, and a rating system. We also provide guidelines for safe meetups and contactless exchanges.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: What types of toilet paper can I trade on the app?

FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: How do I set pricing for my toilet paper listings?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: You have full control over your pricing. Check current market trends within the app, consider factors like brand and quantity, and set competitive prices to attract buyers.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: What if I encounter issues during a trade?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Our dedicated support team is here to help! If you experience any problems during a trade, use the in-app support feature to report issues. We'll work quickly to resolve any concerns and ensure a smooth trading experience.
